==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ɪˈklɛktɪk/}}, {{SAMPA|/I"klEktIk/}}

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|éclectique|lang=fr}} from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἐκλεκτικός||selective|tr=eklektikos|lang=grc}} from {{term|ἐκλέγω||I pick, choose|tr=eklegō|lang=grc}} from {{term|ἐκ||out, from|tr=ek|lang=grc}} + {{term|λέγω||I choose, count|tr=legō|lang=grc}}.

Cognate to {{term|elect|lang=en}}, which is from {{la}} rather than {{grc}}, hence prefix {{term|e-|lang=la}} (from {{term|ex|lang=la}}) rather than {{term|ἐκ|tr=ek|lang=grc}}.

